title: Default values are not shown in Show Report Parameters' dialog
description: Default values are not displayed in the 'Show Report Parameters' dialog box.
OB: When opening the 'Show Report Parameters' dialog box, the default values for the parameters are not shown.
EB: When opening the 'Show Report Parameters' dialog box, the default values for the parameters should be displayed.
SR:
1. Open the application.
2. Navigate to the 'Show Report Parameters' dialog box.
3. Check if the default values for the parameters are displayed.
